Condition.name: VC4_Abs_PartRevision_RestrictDatasetType_Revise
Condition.expression: so.object_type="UGMASTER" OR so.object_type="UGPART" OR so.object_type="DrawingSheet" OR so.object_type="DirectModel"
Condition.description: Restrict dataset types while on Revise operation other than UGMASTER,UGPART,DrawingSheet,DirectModel

Condition.name: VC4_Abs_PartRevision_RestrictDatasetType_SaveAs
Condition.description: Restrict dataset types while on SaveAs operation other than UGMASTER,UGPART

Condition.name: VC4_TDRDisplayForGroupsVolocopterDBAOnly
Condition.description: If user is neither member of group dba, nor belonging to subgroups of Volocopter group, the each of the expressions return true. True AND true will result in true and therefore hide the correspnding object for creation.

Condition.name: VC4_ProjectDocRevOnly_WF
Condition.expression: (o != null) AND ((o.object_type = "VC4_VPF_DocRevision") OR (o.object_type = "VC4_VPI_DocRevision") OR (o.object_type = "VC4_VPP_DocRevision") OR (o.object_type = "VC4_VPS_DocRevision") OR (o.object_type = "VC4_DQA_DocRevision"))

Condition.name: VC4_WF_CN_Process_WF
Condition.expression: (o != null) AND (o.object_type = "VC4_CNRevision") AND (Condition::VC4_GroupConfigurationManagementOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) AND (Condition::VC4_StatusLastReleaseStatusNull_WF (o, t, u) = true)

Condition.name: VC4_WF_CR_Process_WF
Condition.expression: (o != null) AND (o.object_type = "VC4_CRRevision") AND (Condition::VC4_StatusLastReleaseStatusNull_WF (o, t, u) = true)

Condition.name: VC4_WF_Commercial_Part_Release_WF
Condition.expression: (o != null) AND (o.object_type = "CommercialPart Revision") AND (Condition::VC4_GroupStandardPartsOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) AND (Condition::VC4_StatusLastReleaseStatusNull_WF (o, t, u) = true)

Condition.name: VC4_WF_ECM_Document_Release_WF
Condition.expression: (Condition::VC4_ECMDocRevOnly_WF(o, t, u) = true) AND(Condition::VC4_StatusLastReleaseStatusNull_WF(o, t, u) = true)

Condition.name: VC4_WF_Hide_WF
Condition.description: If this condition is attached to a WF, the template will not be displayed in the New Process Dialog for any user. This condition is meant to be attached to OOTB WFs which are not relevant for the business.

Condition.name: VC4_WF_Make_Part_Or_Document_Obsolete_WF
Condition.expression: ((Condition::VC4_AbsQMSDocRevOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) OR (Condition::VC4_AbsProductDocRevOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) OR (Condition::VC4_AbsPartRevOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true)) AND ((Condition::VC4_GroupConfigurationManagementOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) OR (Condition::VC4_GroupDBAOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true)) AND ((Condition::VC4_StatusApproved_WF (o, t, u) = true) OR (Condition::VC4_StatusPrototypeReleased_WF (o, t, u) = true))

Condition.name: VC4_WF_Part_Prototype_Release_WF
Condition.expression: (Condition::VC4_AbsPartRevOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) AND (Condition::VC4_StatusLastReleaseStatusNull_WF (o, t, u) = true)

Condition.name: VC4_WF_Product_Document_Release_WF
Condition.expression: (Condition::VC4_AbsProductDocRevOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) AND (Condition::VC4_StatusLastReleaseStatusNull_WF (o, t, u) = true)

Condition.name: VC4_WF_Project_Document_Release_WF
Condition.expression: (Condition::VC4_ProjectDocRevOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) AND (Condition::VC4_StatusLastReleaseStatusNull_WF (o, t, u) = true)

Condition.name: VC4_WF_QMS_Document_Release_WF
Condition.expression: (Condition::VC4_AbsQMSDocRevOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) AND (Condition::VC4_StatusLastReleaseStatusNull_WF (o, t, u) = true)

Condition.name: VC4_WF_RDD_Release_WF
Condition.expression: (Condition::VC4_AbsPartRevOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) AND (Condition::VC4_StatusLastReleaseStatusNull_WF (o, t, u) = true)

Condition.name: VC4_WF_TCM_Document_Release_WF
Condition.expression: (Condition::VC4_TCMDocRevOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) AND (Condition::VC4_StatusLastReleaseStatusNull_WF (o, t, u) = true)

Condition.name: VC4_WF_TDD_Release_WF
Condition.expression: (Condition::VC4_AbsPartRevOnly_WF (o, t, u) = true) AND (Condition::VC4_StatusLastReleaseStatusNull_WF (o, t, u) = true)

Condition.name: isChangeExecutionAllowed
Condition.expression: o.CMClosure = "Open" AND o.CMMaturity != "Reviewing" AND u.fnd0ConditionHelper.fnd0isSubTypeOf(o, "GnChangeNoticeRevision") AND ( Condition::isAnalyst(o, u) OR o.fnd0IsParticipant("Cm0ChangeContributors") OR Condition::isRequestor(o, u))
Condition.description: This condition determines if Change Execution is allowed.

Condition.name: Cm0isCMHasSolutionItemCreatable
Condition.description: To add Solution Items the user must have authoring license level, be Analyst, Change Contributor or Requestor (= Change Specialist for Volocopter CN process), have write access to the change item and it must be in Open & not Reviewing state.
